data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 11/4/23 from 11:00-11:30AM. 1517 Riverside is a beautiful home that sits in a very nice and quiet neighborhood in Verona, PA! This property has incredible features including a NEWER ROOF, OFF STREET PARKING SPOT, a LARGE KITCHEN with plenty of room for storage, and HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT. The bathroom has recently been updated, and there is a NEWER roof at the property. All the bedrooms are sizeable, and there is a gorgeous back deck that creates the perfect entertainment space! Located less than 30 minutes from Downtown Pittsburgh and easy access to major roadway 376 and makes this the perfect opportunity for end buyers everywhere!
